{"tid":2453324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有私家醫生張貼告示指科興疫苗「聲譽不好」，惹建制團體抨擊","createTime":"2021-03-19T11:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T18:12:42.000Z","uid":5195,"like":837,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"9a38538aa358a7a248c621bddf196ac31a8fb7f8","tid":2453324,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210319/449621853900640256506872.jpeg/rPpGqDZ2p22e9q18IuObpqG1hrmA7aJ-n2JIm59iSJs?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210319%2F449621853900640256506872.jpeg%2FrPpGqDZ2p22e9q18IuObpqG1hrmA7aJ-n2JIm59iSJs%3Fv%3Dw960&h=8e93dd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍土瓜灣私家醫生劉東華的診所自製表格，指科興「聲譽不好」，復必泰則「國際聲譽良好」，亦表示醫生自己及政府專家顧問袁國勇教授都「不打」科興。相關言論惹建制團體抨擊，揚言向醫委會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該醫生列出疫苗有效率的資料，與政府資訊相符；科興在內地曾涉賄賂事件確有其事。診所已撤下表格，護士引述醫生稱無補充。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇回應表示，兩種疫苗的效能和質素，民眾應該按照個人情況，選擇接種。<br />\n<br />\n記者今日（19日）傍晚到劉東華的診所，發現該表格已被撤下。診所護士表示，劉醫生無補充。<br />\n<br />\n引述科興賄賂舊聞　稱其「聲譽不好」<br />\n<br />\n據網上照片，位於九龍土瓜灣私家醫生劉東華的診所，內有表格比較了「科興」及「復必泰」兩種疫苗，如指出科興有效率最高為50％，復必泰則有95％，及指兩種疫苗副作用「大致相同」。同時，表格亦指出科興「聲譽不好」，復必泰則「國際聲譽良好」。<br />\n<br />\n表格有進一步解釋，科興之所以「聲譽不好」，原因是「曾用了55萬元賄賂中國藥品監督管理局官員尹紅章，讓科興生產的疫苗得以加快批准使用」，但就沒有解釋為何復必泰「國際聲譽良好」。<br />\n<br />\n事件引來親建制團體抨擊，認為內容抹黑「科興」疫苗、「恐嚇」市民，有違醫德，會向醫委會投訴要求徹查。"},{"pid":"e44d95ac8eca00fadc2948b36af9b9d1e3d0b378","tid":2453324,"uid":290118,"like":390,"dislike":1,"score":389,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"講事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d651e11f05f8a5262551cacc6bb4dcf99e8f80a","tid":2453324,"uid":390358,"like":260,"dislike":0,"score":260,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"關醫德咩事<br />\n藍支狗要打地溝油鹽水都要畀佢打㗎啦<br />\n決定權仲喺簽名嗰個到<br />\n<br />\n利申咩都唔會打"},{"pid":"2c93ad61eef2bf1a05318f4fe101f0a704142ff9","tid":2453324,"uid":267494,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"樣樣都係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc802dc588d01913dae471fc964f581a4ba294e6","tid":2453324,"uid":171107,"like":120,"dislike":2,"score":118,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:36:43.000Z","msg":"以後唔舒服去佢度睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f69f9ad84dc06ba1a1189a384ec53aef6ef090","tid":2453324,"uid":11663,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但就沒有解釋為何復必泰「國際聲譽良好」。</blockquote><br />\n點解仲要解釋為何良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e27785d64147b90cada189f34ccc7d2920ab06b","tid":2453324,"uid":76310,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"劉醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf35a02d8ed38a701e4df16d110f6ecf41d2824","tid":2453324,"uid":242537,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lk7GSGc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLk7GSGc.gif&h=976c118b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e27a3981b3c75144ef70d2f9f502f404e505e367","tid":2453324,"uid":292644,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:36:08.000Z","msg":"正宗「黃」醫生"},{"pid":"818cded3fe11f12d6b0a8da1b20587a7fa6753f0","tid":2453324,"uid":335967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T12:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /