佢睇左好多年<br />\n佢好有耐性問診好細心 雖然年紀比較大<br />\n但講醫德佢絕對有<br />\n佢用意係想簡單提示老人家打邊隻針好者<br />\n班仆街藍屍又玻璃心  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85d5a7ebadafded09d12bb7742ece7632a83f51","tid":2453324,"uid":89683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:06:41.000Z","msg":"而家批評支那嘅事實就有建制團體打壓，無人理嘅　？"},{"pid":"dd2cd7a1e5409eaccaff7fde7be43191c5311cdb","tid":2453324,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"投訴囉 全部事實有灑數據新聞 一陣醫委會睇完話無問題 建制就柒到飛天 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee327f6a5320e0817f3ea94b16d7801acc5b7e71","tid":2453324,"uid":383943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a38538aa358a7a248c621bddf196ac31a8fb7f8","tid":2453324,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T11:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210319/449621853900640256506872.jpeg/rPpGqDZ2p22e9q18IuObpqG1hrmA7aJ-n2JIm59iSJs?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210319%2F449621853900640256506872.jpeg%2FrPpGqDZ2p22e9q18IuObpqG1hrmA7aJ-n2JIm59iSJs%3Fv%3Dw960&h=8e93dd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍土瓜灣私家醫生劉東華的診所自製表格，指科興「聲譽不好」，復必泰則「國際聲譽良好」，亦表示醫生自己及政府專家顧問袁國勇教授都「不打」科興。相關言論惹建制團體抨擊，揚言向醫委會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該醫生列出疫苗有效率的資料，與政府資訊相符；科興在內地曾涉賄賂事件確有其事。診所已撤下表格，護士引述醫生稱無補充。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇回應表示，兩種疫苗的效能和質素，民眾應該按照個人情況，選擇接種。<br />\n<br />\n記者今日（19日）傍晚到劉東華的診所，發現該表格已被撤下。診所護士表示，劉醫生無補充。<br />\n<br />\n引述科興賄賂舊聞　稱其「聲譽不好」<br />\n<br />\n據網上照片，位於九龍土瓜灣私家醫生劉東華的診所，內有表格比較了「科興」及「復必泰」兩種疫苗，如指出科興有效率最高為50％，復必泰則有95％，及指兩種疫苗副作用「大致相同」。同時，表格亦指出科興「聲譽不好」，復必泰則「國際聲譽良好」。<br />\n<br />\n表格有進一步解釋，科興之所以「聲譽不好」，原因是「曾用了55萬元賄賂中國藥品監督管理局官員尹紅章，讓科興生產的疫苗得以加快批准使用」，但就沒有解釋為何復必泰「國際聲譽良好」。<br />\n<br />\n事件引來親建制團體抨擊，認為內容抹黑「科興」疫苗、「恐嚇」市民，有違醫德，會向醫委會投訴要求徹查。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔加埋「科興：許樹昌、不打」？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8e72c4719a152f2fcdf20d04863879caf83d85","tid":2453324,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:16:34.000Z","msg":"大大聲叫人問醫生意見，醫生講意見又要投訴，愛國果然係大撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44fa1d05cc7a3925fc8ac7be3d5f74303c015e7","tid":2453324,"uid":322130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"事實投訴撚都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5467f9cad7ec8053216123964b41fd15dd3e7bf8","tid":2453324,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022c2b2477c55e4b0745aec55159a84886604e67","tid":2453324,"uid":300877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"good doctor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3a203f2fe9c56793b50a26b49a2cc21710febe","tid":2453324,"uid":272696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"忠誠廢物抹黑社會精英<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4fa23b7a47a99e472cde682da64925497eca73","tid":2453324,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"科興就係狗"},{"pid":"4d6ca309e9e827cbbe32c0b9bef740bbbe89282f","tid":2453324,"uid":28834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"講事實又唔岩聽 人地又唔係屈你 點樣叫無醫德呀？"},{"pid":"f8468ca2d08ec5e579554575fa8e9a5205603626","tid":24533